Open a Decision record page.

Click on the Approval tab after data loads.

Click on the Acknowledgement tab after data loads.

Log in with a user who has restricted field/object permissions.

Approval and Acknowledgement tabs are displayed.

Approvals are shown only for that Decision with columns: Date, Stage, Assigned To, Actual Approval Date.

Acknowledgements are shown only for that Decision with columns: Date, Stage, Assigned To, Actual Acknowledger, Comment.

User cannot see restricted data or fields.
